ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectGeneral Coordination Agreement Between Canada and the United States of America on the Use of the Radio Frequency Spectrum by Terrestrial Radiocommunication Stations and Earth Stations
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to BRING INTO FORCE for Canada the GENERAL COORDINATION AGREEMENT BETWEEN CANADA AND THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA ON THE USE OF THE RADIO FREQUENCY SPECTRUM BY TERRESTRIAL RADIOCOMMUNICATION STATIONS AND EARTH STATIONS, done at Ottawa on January 12 and 13, 2021.
